description:
DESIGN GOALS

 * Singleton format but functional reprints are OK.
 * Intended for playing in paper. Cards and combos with excessive tracking requirements are avoided.
 * No initiative, dual-faced, silver-bordered, draft-matters, ante, or conspiracy cards (some might make it in occasionally).
 * Support aggro, midrange, control, and combo strategies.
 * Support synergy archetypes such as artifacts, lands, and stax.

OUR DRAFT METHOD
When drafting with N number of players, randomly select floor(45*N/8) cards from each section (W, U, B, R, G, multicolor, colorless, and lands) to help even out color distribution and provide strong mana fixing. Shuffle all selected cards together and then make packs.
